QuestData.Title: Admiral Taylor
QuestData.Description: Admiral Taylor had figured out who was behind all this. He told us to save who we could... he wanted to handle matters himself.$B$BWe never heard from him again, but we have our orders.$B$BPlease... please find him. He went towards the farm.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Admiral Taylor at Admiral Taylor's Farm.
QuestData.RewardText: From one commander to another... thank you.$B$BWe've faced off on the field of battle so many times. Vashj'ir... the Jade Forest... Lion's Landing...$B$BI am glad I could end my journey with such a worthy adversary.
